{"tid":1854041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(厲害了 進口国) 中国一週進口逾5000萬個口罩","createTime":"2020-01-31T09:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T09:59:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"88283835a4098270023a749ebf261776c657ad89","tid":1854041,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:49:54.000Z","msg":"受武漢肺炎疫情影響，中國官方公布，過去一週共進口了5622.8萬個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n中國海關總署今天發布消息指出，自1月24日至30日，共進口疫情防控物資1萬6139批、5917.8萬件，價值人民幣2.9億元（新台幣約12.7億元）。<br />\n<br />\n其中，口罩5622.8萬個，護目鏡6.9萬副，防護服73.8萬件，藥品10.7萬盒，消毒物品3.6萬件，醫療器械9.5萬件。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國官方最新統計，2019新型冠狀病毒（2019-nCoV）引起的武漢肺炎死亡病例在中國全境已達213例，單日新增確診病例數近2000例，累計共9692例，預期今天將破萬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202001310256.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202001310256.aspx&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=c1d18a9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202001310256.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"c7aeae1e0b0b1d203692705ccd3afc2a4ee581aa","tid":1854041,"uid":138594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 搶就搶啦 <br />\n明明成班賊偷龍轉鳳<br />\n進你老母閪個口啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5680f0646502ba5ad048c57a234b7645bbb0f0c","tid":1854041,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:59:31.000Z","msg":"5000 萬個唔夠佢POPOULATAION用1日..."}]}